fy: A word which expresses blame dislike disapprobation abhorrence or contempt See Fie
fyke: A long bag net distended by hoops into which fish can pass easily without being able to return called also fyke net Cozzens
fyllot: A rebated cross formerly used as a secret emblem and a common ornament It is also called gammadion and swastika
fyrd: The military force of the whole nation consisting of all men able to bear arms The national fyrd or militia J R Green
fyrdung: The military force of the whole nation consisting of all men able to bear arms The national fyrd or militia J R Green
